    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2>复刻经典回合制策略棋牌玩法，在这个马太效应和随机漫步交叉运作的世界里，玩家需要合理利用有限的存款、现金、道具和随机事件，争取在对抗中积累原始资本，巩固自己的经济权力，成为每局对抗赛中的胜利者。当然，你也可以放下胜负心，邀请好友进行一场谁也猜不到下一步的欢乐对局，体验这变幻莫测的局势。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395810/extras/6739a5c7b892f7264a33c6ea10440b60.poster.avif?t=1725033396\" width=618 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395810/extras/6739a5c7b892f7264a33c6ea10440b60.webm?t=1725033396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395810/extras/6739a5c7b892f7264a33c6ea10440b60.mp4?t=1725033396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2>玩家通过选择代入不同的动物城居民；在地图中存在着十二生肖神明和通灵师这样的超自然npc，与不同的npc接触便可能将战局拖向更大的变数；除了每种建筑都功能不同，某些特殊场地还设置有隐藏npc如黑客、政府高官，所谓福祸相依，在玩家意想不到的地方说不定能绝地翻盘。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395810/extras/f188edc04d7e85de8c8e246cd6b526b0.poster.avif?t=1725033396\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395810/extras/f188edc04d7e85de8c8e246cd6b526b0.webm?t=1725033396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395810/extras/f188edc04d7e85de8c8e246cd6b526b0.mp4?t=1725033396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创意工坊</h2>派对游戏的可玩性不应局限于游戏本身，基于这一立场，我们希望开放创意工坊并支持玩家在游戏框架上实现他们的独特想法。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏包含</h2>10个图形NPC，14种建筑，8张地图，8个动物城居民角色和12个附身神仙角色<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395810/extras/5f19d771837c9a2205d7c372bfd44e8f.poster.avif?t=1725033396\" width=618 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395810/extras/5f19d771837c9a2205d7c372bfd44e8f.webm?t=1725033396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395810/extras/5f19d771837c9a2205d7c372bfd44e8f.mp4?t=1725033396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >联系我们</h2>ᕙ(•̤᷆ ॒ ູ•̤᷇)ᕘ₊˚<br>官方①群：<br>官方②群：597683207<br>官方③群：224984920<br>官方④群：885392988",
